{
  "stem": "4361.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the older girls-- older girls, two, three year older, older than I-- belonged to the Barisia, which was a step forward.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And but Jewish life was good in the sense that they-- the Jews very permitted-- there was no obstacle to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Business was closed during Saturday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The main street, the corso, was full of-- around 12:00, noon time-- it was full of Jews coming from synagogues, after synagogue, having a walk on the corso.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Business stopped during Saturdays.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm talking about the Romanian regime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sighet was-- [LAUGHS] today we would consider it a little village, but it was not really a village.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had about 50,000 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were Jews, Hungarians, and Romanians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews were about between 12,000 and 15,000 Jews, and the rest was a mix-- mixture of ethnic Hungarians and Romanians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "During the Romanian regime, I do not remember any anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Things went along nicely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father was a well-known and respected businessman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- he was in textile, and his specialty were silks, as another businessman's specialty were woolens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my father's specialty was silk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a very comfortable, to say the least, household in which I grew up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the Romanian regime, there was no relationship because, first of all, they were minorities.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this would eventually change in 1940 when the Hungarians took over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the relationship with the Romanians was a very good relationship in the sense that it was a practical relationship.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember the name what it was called.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, it was the Jewish community with a president, with a-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My uncle was at one time the [NON-ENGLISH], and my uncle was a very stern man.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
